gamerules.gamerules2: Base Game is a 1 Line Game
gamerules.highestWin: Only the highest win pays perline
gamerules.Re_spin_Rule: When two WILDS appear on any two reels along with a blank on the other reel, the blank Reel will have a Re-Spin feature, where that reel will spin again to land a non blank symbol and assures a win.
gamerules.randomWildMulText: Whenever a wild lands, there is a chance it may award a amultiplier. So, whenever a wild lands, every 30 spins a multiplier is awarded from 5x ,8x or 10x.
